snippet.title: Amber Heard for Glamour USA January 2019
snippet.description:
Amber Heard is on the cover of Glamour USA last printed issue, January 2019. The editorial was shot by Jason Kibbler and you can watch the photos in our website and photo gallery.

Check out our photo gallery: www.amberhearditalia.com/galleria
